# Gowid (고위드)

**Last Updated:** 2026-03-07

## Company Overview
- **Sector:** B2B Fintech SaaS
- **Revenue:** W1,493B (cumulative W1,000B+ milestone reached)
- **Status:** Active, IPO target 2025-2026

